    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>d738563dex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EX-99.1\n<TEXT>\n<HTML><HEAD>\n<TITLE>EX-99.1</TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n <BODY BGCOLOR=\"WHITE\">\n\n <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\" ALIGN=\"right\"><B>Exhibit 99.1 </B></P> <P STYLE=\"font-size:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" WIDTH=\"100%\" BORDER=\"0\" STYLE=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:COLLAPSE; font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt\" ALIGN=\"center\">\n\n\n<TR>\n<TD WIDTH=\"33%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"1%\"></TD>\n<TD WIDTH=\"34%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"1%\"></TD>\n<TD WIDTH=\"31%\"></TD></TR>\n\n\n<TR STYLE=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt\">\n<TD VALIGN=\"top\"> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B>TSX</B>: CCO</P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:1pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B>NYS</B><B>E</B>:\nCCJ</P></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\">&nbsp;</TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"top\" ALIGN=\"center\">\n\n\n<IMG SRC=\"g738563g26k60.jpg\" ALT=\"LOGO\">\n</TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"top\"> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B></B><B>website: </B>cameco.com</P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:1pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B></B><B>currency:</B> Cdn (unless noted)<B></B></P></TD></TR>\n</TABLE> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\" ALIGN=\"center\">2121 &#150; 11<SUP STYLE=\"font-size:85%; vertical-align:top\">th </SUP>Street West, Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, S7M\n1J3 Canada </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\" ALIGN=\"center\">Tel: (306)&nbsp;956-6200 Fax: (306)&nbsp;956-6201 </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\" ALIGN=\"center\"><B>Cameco Announces Election of Directors </B></P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\">Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, Canada, May&nbsp;30, 2014 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B>Cameco</B> (TSX: CCO; NYSE: CCJ) has announced the election of 13 board members at its annual meeting held on May&nbsp;28, 2014. </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\">Shareholders elected board members Ian Bruce, Daniel Camus, John Clappison, Joe Colvin, James Curtiss, Donald Deranger, Catherine Gignac, Tim Gitzel, James\nGowans, Nancy Hopkins, Anne McLellan, Neil McMillan and Victor Zaleschuk. (Voting results are available below) </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B>Voting Results for Cameco Directors\n</B></P> <P STYLE=\"font-size:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" WIDTH=\"100%\" BORDER=\"0\" STYLE=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:COLLAPSE; font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt\" ALIGN=\"center\">\n\n\n<TR>\n<TD WIDTH=\"70%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"2%\"></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"2%\"></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"2%\"></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"2%\"></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD>\n<TD></TD></TR>\n<TR STYLE=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:8pt\">\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" NOWRAP> <P STYLE=\"border-bottom:1.00pt solid #000000; width:30.20pt; font-size:8pt; font-family:Times New Roman\"><B>Nominee</B></P></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" COLSPAN=\"2\" ALIGN=\"center\" STYLE=\"border-bottom:1.00pt solid #000000\"><B>Votes For</B></TD